<p>
  <strong>--Collection of Information--</strong>
</p>
<p>
  <strong>Information You Provide to Us</strong>
</p>
<p>
  We collect information you provide directly to us through MeetingSlice or
  otherwise. For example, we collect information when you create a
  MeetingSlice account, setup your profile, search the MeetingSlice
  directory, send a message, request a meeting, book a meeting, request
