  MeetingSlice. The types of information we may collect include your name,
  email address, city and state, phone number, payment method information,
  resume information, demographic and biographical information, and any other
  information you choose to provide.
</p>
<p>
  <strong>
    Information We Collect Automatically When You Use the Services
  </strong>
</p>
<p>
  When you access or use our Services, we automatically collect information
  about you, including:
</p>
<p>
  • <strong>Log Information:</strong> We collect log information in
  connection with your use of the Services, including the type of browser you
