  hardware model, operating system and version, unique device identifiers and
  mobile network information.
</p>
<p>
  • <strong>Location Information:</strong> We may collect information about
  your location through various technologies, including by deriving
  approximate location from IP address and by collecting more precise
  location via our mobile apps.
</p>
<p>
  <strong>
    Information Collected by Cookies and Other Tracking Technologies:
  </strong>
