  information, including cookies and web beacons. Cookies are small data
  files stored on your hard drive or in device memory that help us improve
  our Services and your experience, see which areas and features of our
  Services are popular and count visits. Web beacons are electronic images
  that may be used in our Services or emails and help deliver cookies, count
  visits and understand usage and campaign effectiveness.
</p>
