<p>
  <strong>--Your Choices—</strong>
</p>
<p>
  <strong>Account Information</strong>
  <br/>
  You may update your account information by logging into your online
  account. If you wish to delete account information, you may log into your
  account to delete this information, but note that we may retain certain
  information as required by law or for legitimate business purposes. We may
  also retain cached or archived copies of information about you for a
  certain period of time.
</p>
<p>
  <strong>Location Information</strong>
  <br/>
  If you initially consent to our collection of location information from our
  mobile apps, you can subsequently stop the collection of this information
  by changing the preferences on your mobile device. If you do so, our mobile
  apps, or certain features thereof, may no longer function. You may also
  stop our collection of location information by following the standard
  uninstall process to remove our mobile apps from your device.
</p>
<p>
  <strong>Cookies</strong>
  <br/>
  Most web browsers are set to accept cookies by default. If you prefer, you
  can usually choose to set your browser to remove or reject browser cookies.
  Please note that if you choose to remove or reject cookies, this could
  affect the availability and functionality of our websites.
</p>
<p>
  <strong>Promotional Communications</strong>
  <br/>
  You may opt out of receiving promotional messages from Company by following
  the instructions in those messages. If you opt out, we may still send you
  non-promotional communications, such as those about your account or our
  ongoing business relations.
</p>
<p>
  <strong>Mobile Push Notifications/Alerts</strong>
  <br/>
  With your consent, we may send promotional and non-promotional push
  notifications or alerts to your mobile device. Such notifications are used,
  for example, to alert you about incoming messages, payment disbursements
  made to you, deadlines to respond to messages and so on. You can deactivate
  these messages at any time by changing the notification settings on your
  mobile device.
